            <title>[SUREFIRE-300] NPE in SurefirePlugin.constructSurefireBooter()</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-300</link>
                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SurefirePlugin.constructSurefireBooter() throws NPE when no testcases are present in the project. The log attached is from building FtpServer admin-gui using the 2.3 version of maven-surefire-plugin:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/incubator/ftpserver/trunk/admin-gui/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/incubator/ftpserver/trunk/admin-gui/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
